quote.summary: Hangzhou Jiuyuan Genetic Biopharmaceutical Co Ltd, formerly Hangzhou Jiuyuan Gene Engineering Co Ltd, is a China-based company principally engaged in the research, development, manufacturing and commercialization of biopharmaceutical products and medical devices. The Company focuses on orthopedics, metabolic diseases, oncology and blood treatment. The Company's orthopedic products include Guyoudao bone repair materials. The Company's oncology products include Jilifen, Jijufen, Jiouting, Jifuwei, and Jitansu. The Company's blood products include Jipailin and Yinuojia. The Company's products are mainly used to treat diseases such as diabetes, multiple myeloma, thrombocytopenia, and neutropenia. The Company mainly operates its businesses in the domestic and overseas markets.
